Package: htmxr
Title: Build Modern Web Applications with htmx and plumber2
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Arthur", "BrÃ©ant", , "arthur@thinkr.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A lightweight framework for building server-driven web
    applications in R. htmxr combines the simplicity of htmx for partial
    page updates with the power of plumber2 for non-blocking HTTP
    endpoints. Build interactive dashboards and data applications without
    writing JavaScript, using familiar R patterns inspired by Shiny.
